# handoff-redesign — local ignore (export 結果 / handoff bundle のみ)
# root .gitignore は触らない (prompt pack 本体は git tracked、PR review 対象)

# Phase 1A/B export
*-output.html
*-output.pdf
*-output.png
*-export.*

# Phase 1C handoff bundle (Claude Design の "Send to Claude Code" 結果)
99-claude-code-handoff/bundle/

# upload-once の user 任意 export
00-shared/upload-once/*-export.*
00-shared/upload-once/prototype-screenshot-*.png
00-shared/upload-once/prototype-screenshot-*.jpg
